text: Neighbourhood convenient store with a wide selection of goods. Strong aircon. Run by a very friendly family.

Really great minimart. Stocked with lots of stuff. Owners are very friendly; always greeting and talking to us like old friends.

There is a rotating list discounted items changing every day. Giving incentive to go see them.
Great minimart with very attractive pricing. You will be surprise most item is cheaper than big name supermarkets and i mean way cheaper.

My favorite minimart!! The store owner and his family are so friendly! I always enjoy patronizing the shop. It’s also very accessible. They also have a wide variety of items that can’t be found in some other minimarts.  Thumbs up!!
Very friendly staff, wide range of varieties at very reasonable prices. You won't get these prices at big supermarket franchises.
